{"tid":1893322,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動] 集結連登力量2.0 名校Secrets戰線 - 抵制奶共名校Secrets","createTime":"2020-02-23T07:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T21:56:42.000Z","uid":200794,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c34f755c0f80ed2ab57b7119e13fa9e30235a8a8","tid":1893322,"uid":200794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:32:20.000Z","msg":"原post: ［告急］名校secret戰線要人啊 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1887715/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1887715/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nTLDR：<br />\n名校Secrets死灰復燃，並成為三毛之地，更疑被經濟日報收購，正式染紅<br />\n為打救一眾中學生，各位連登巴絲打係時候發動攻勢，以免名校Secrets繼續荼毒中學生<br />\n<br />\n1. 抵制名校Secrets<br />\n- Unlike + Report Facebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/schools.secrets/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fschools.secrets%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=f97db365\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/schools.secrets/</a><br />\n- Unfollow + Report ig ac: @schools.secrets <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/schools.secrets/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fschools.secrets%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=a984f10c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/schools.secrets/</a><br />\n- 喺名校Secrets Facebook &amp; Instagram留言關於御學軒醜聞嘅資料<br />\n- 去Play Store同App Store為Schoolmates app俾1星同留comment<br />\nPlay Store: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=es.schoolmat\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Des.schoolmat&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=f8d83d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=es.schoolmat</a> <br />\nApp Store無link<br />\n網頁版: <a href=\"https://schoolmat.es/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fschoolmat.es%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=dc1eb4a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://schoolmat.es/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HGfMS28.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHGfMS28.png&h=4442c225&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n <br />\n2. 支持新名校Secrets<br />\n- Like Facebook page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/new.school.secrets.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnew.school.secrets.hk&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=f538b38f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/new.school.secrets.hk</a><br />\n- Follow ig: @new.school.secrets.hk <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/new.school.secrets.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnew.school.secrets.hk%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=9942e794\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/new.school.secrets.hk/</a><br />\n- Follow Twitter: @new_school_hk <a href=\"https://twitter.com/new_school_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnew_school_hk&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=99fa99cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/new_school_hk</a><br />\n- 推介身邊嘅同學朋友轉用新名校Secrets<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQ5AMk4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQ5AMk4.png&h=4008368d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">麻煩大家整多啲文宣share出去</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tC1DJ70.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtC1DJ70.png&h=74bf04f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gP4NCs4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgP4NCs4.png&h=e68c8ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n事源: <br />\n大家記唔記得兩年前連登嘅呢一個post<br />\n集結連登力量 向名校secrets開戰 後續行動更新以及事件完整整合（8）- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/616106\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/616106</a><br />\n<br />\n當日大家發現名校Secrets原來由一間公司 - <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>御學軒(一間專門開辦升中面試及升小面試課程嘅教育中心)</strong></span>喺幕後操控住，會過濾河蟹甚至亂改投稿內容，亂咁block人同block哂所有不利佢地嘅comments，令到名校Secrets以及其附屬app&mdash;&mdash;Schoolmates被大家唾棄，一度進入瀕死狀態。<br />\n當大家以爲名校Secrets從此喺網絡上消失，但殊不知其實名校Secrets一直無收皮到，而且背後操控住名校Secrets嘅公司更加疑似經過易手而變得撲朔迷離。<br />\n為免名校Secrets繼續荼毒中學生，洗佢地腦，我希望可以再次集結連登力量，狙擊名校Secrets，令呢個page正式收皮！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>2020名校Secrets事件整合</ins><br />\n1. 名校Secrets被PR公司iLeague Digital Company Limited (網連數碼有限公司)收購，多次分享藍媒﹑紅媒新聞<br />\n喺御學軒事件後，大概2018年5月，名校Secrets開始出現新聞連結，當中大部分都係藍媒，有香港01﹑東網﹑星島頭條網等<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8u2rpH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8u2rpH.png&h=b16d6367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年7月6號開始，名校Secrets開始post大量TOPick嘅新聞，而其餘嘅就嚟自Business Focus<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/owiR4c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FowiR4c6.png&h=e7900a60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTOPick屬於經濟日報，佢地嘅前副社長石鏡泉曾經喺撐警大會上表示 「教仔」須用藤條及水喉通，結果第二日就發生元朗721事件<br />\nBusiness Focus屬於PressLogic，根據立場新聞，PressLogic2017年獲內地手機App美圖(1357)入股；美圖公司首席財務官顏勁良於2018年5月加入PressLogic的營運公司，出任公司董事<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%90%8D%E6%A0%A1secrets-%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E5%88%AA%E6%96%87%E6%83%B9%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9-%E9%81%AD%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E6%88%96%E7%94%B1%E5%8D%87%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1secrets-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%25E5%2588%25AA%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%2589%25B9-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%2594%25B1%25E5%258D%2587%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2587%259F%25E9%2581%258B%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=855bc83d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1secrets-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%25E5%2588%25AA%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%2589%25B9-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%2594%25B1%25E5%258D%2587%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2587%259F%25E9%2581%258B%2F&h=4c2fa3fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%90%8D%E6%A0%A1secrets-%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E5%88%AA%E6%96%87%E6%83%B9%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9-%E9%81%AD%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E6%88%96%E7%94%B1%E5%8D%87%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，新名校 Secrets嘅Admin喺2月20號指名校Secrets由御學軒轉咗手去一間PR公司。//另外，我哋而家有嘅資料係舊名校secret嘅控制權已經唔係喺御學軒手，而係喺間PR公司度。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/471866373333145/posts/813314585854987/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F471866373333145%2Fposts%2F813314585854987%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=ef4d58d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/471866373333145/posts/813314585854987/?sfnsn=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EMSO6r5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEMSO6r5.jpg&h=12c5fd71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據名校 Secrets Facebook page，該公司為iLeague Digital Company Limited (網連數碼有限公司)，於2016年3月23日成立。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URb4ENv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURb4ENv.jpg&h=c7e6d57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 名校Secrets成五毛三毛集中地<br />\n喺7個月前，已經有巴打發現名校Secrets充斥五毛post<br />\n名校secret fb page 湧現大量三毛post - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276242</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MnjFc9y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnjFc9y.png&h=ddb0f906&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有啲五毛post嘅形式通常會話「首先我係黃，xxxxxxx，但燒黨鐵真係好咩，我唔贊成暴力，xxxxxxx。最後光復香港，時代革命。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUN7CB7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUN7CB7.png&h=4dcc6a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">名校Secrets被PR公司收購，經常share藍媒﹑紅媒嘅新聞，再加上有好多五毛post出現，背後目的令人懷疑係想潛移默化咁洗年輕一代腦，所以我地要新增名校Secrets戰線，令到呢個奶共page消失，以免名校Secrets繼續荼毒中學生</span></span>"},{"pid":"aef805531736c4ccd9a4239502fe943bcfbe2df4","tid":1893322,"uid":200794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:33:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>Report教學：</strong><br />\n<ins>Report Facebook Page</ins><br />\n(中文版)<br />\n舉報--&gt; 我認為這不應該出現在 Facebook --&gt; 這是仇恨言論 --&gt; 種族或民族 --&gt; 送交Facebook 審查<br />\n <br />\n(英文版)<br />\nReport --&gt; I think it shouldn't be on Facebook --&gt; It's hate speech --&gt; A race or ethnicity --&gt; Submit to Facebook for review<br />\n <br />\n<ins>Report Instagram Page</ins><br />\n(中文版)<br />\n檢舉 --&gt; 內容不適當 --&gt; I believe this account violates Instagram's community guidelines --&gt; Report account --&gt; Posting inappropriate content --&gt; Hate speech or symbols<br />\n<br />\n(英文版)<br />\nReport --&gt; It's inappropriate --&gt; I believe this account violates Instagram's community guidelines --&gt; Report account --&gt; Posting inappropriate content --&gt; Hate speech or symbols<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>留言參考：</strong><br />\n大概內容：御學軒醜聞資料﹑抵制名校Secrets﹑轉用新名校 Secrets等等<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uty3a0y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUty3a0y.png&h=5aa6bc7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmtKETU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmtKETU.png&h=76901a7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9f636bafcd39a01ac0bd89ac7fe790b02415a92","tid":1893322,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:34:42.000Z","msg":"名校Secrets乜未死架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cef2eb499d9ad5c5e3cb195777569abc8ad475","tid":1893322,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:35:25.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b1d37a839e581e8c70ccac374ab47c6ff06132dd","tid":1893322,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade5f2ed6cdbfab80066443d983b31dfed0f7b34","tid":1893322,"uid":200794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T07:37:15.000Z","msg":"<ins>2018事件回帶</ins> <span style=\"color: red;\">*特別建議唔知當年發生咩事嘅人睇*</span><br />\n2018年4月，名校Secrets Admin刪去一篇關於批判通識教育及使用簡體字的帖文，引起眾多網民聲討，其後被揭發背後由御學軒補習社操控<br />\n<br />\n1. 曲解投稿內容 事後刪帖欲息事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zMJyye8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzMJyye8.png&h=ff61355b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完整事件整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zAtl9kkVNggM0MibIg1l-yAxsMQkCPkOJX-35U6erco/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1zAtl9kkVNggM0MibIg1l-yAxsMQkCPkOJX-35U6erco%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=e609fa83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zAtl9kkVNggM0MibIg1l-yAxsMQkCPkOJX-35U6erco/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n 2. 背後由 御學軒 補習社操控<br />\n全靠連登各位巴打絲打，搵到名校Secrets係屬於御學軒嘅<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%90%8D%E6%A0%A1secrets-%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E5%88%AA%E6%96%87%E6%83%B9%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9-%E9%81%AD%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E6%88%96%E7%94%B1%E5%8D%87%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1secrets-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%25E5%2588%25AA%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%2589%25B9-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%2594%25B1%25E5%258D%2587%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2587%259F%25E9%2581%258B%2F&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=855bc83d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%25A0%25A1secrets-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A0%2581%25E5%2588%25AA%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%2589%25B9-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258F%25AD%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%2594%25B1%25E5%258D%2587%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2587%259F%25E9%2581%258B%2F&h=4c2fa3fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E5%90%8D%E6%A0%A1secrets-%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81%E5%88%AA%E6%96%87%E6%83%B9%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9-%E9%81%AD%E6%8F%AD%E7%99%BC%E6%88%96%E7%94%B1%E5%8D%87%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n追post連結：<br />\n集結連登力量 四月一日夜晚八點向名校secret開戰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/611814/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n<br />\n集結連登力量 四月一日夜晚八點向名校secret開戰（2）<b